=== Inhale System ===

Kirby's signature ability.

{| class="wikitable"
! Action !! Input !! Result
|-
| Inhale || B || Suck in enemies/items
|-
| Swallow || Down + B || Gain copy ability
|-
| Star Spit || B while full || Projectile attack
|-
| Air Puff || B while flying || Small projectile
|}

'''Inhale Properties:'''
* Range: ~3 tiles in front
* Can inhale multiple small enemies
* Large enemies take multiple inhales
* Some enemies cannot be inhaled

