== Stage Structure ==

=== World Layout ===

Each world contains:
* 3-5 regular stages
* 1 Museum (copy ability source)
* 1 Arena (mini-boss battle)
* 1 Boss stage

=== Stage Elements ===

{| class="wikitable"
! Element !! Function
|-
| Door || Enter sub-areas
|-
