|-
| Warp Star || Stage transition
|}

=== Secrets ===

'''Hidden Switches:'''
* Each world has hidden switches
* Unlock bonus stages
* Reveal 100% completion items

'''Big Switches:'''
* Located in hidden rooms
* Unlock new areas in all worlds
* Required for 100%

